{"tid":2155872,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"人到莊年，但係腎虧，點算好？","createTime":"2020-08-14T05:29:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T03:50:05.000Z","uid":172589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"276724bda43f8bd4e3f760a37e9725c6503dc85b","tid":2155872,"uid":172589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:29:26.000Z","msg":"小弟今年27歲，20頭果時仲好地地<br />\n做咗幾年野之後就成日要去廁所<br />\n飲少少水就痾好多果隻<br />\n最老尷係開會present果陣中途忍唔住要交水費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似痾極都仲有咁 點算好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近排仲多咗夜尿，搞到成個人坐唔安訓唔落<br />\n我唔想哩世人都痴住個廁所啊！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af73c8405c15316dce24da31e801f4debb13ca2","tid":2155872,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:30:57.000Z","msg":"睇醫生 運動"},{"pid":"4c9c3bf2f58be2d9c542a6bd624892c56d9f4a49","tid":2155872,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:31:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HcSwQTaIOBk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHcSwQTaIOBk&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=709d8977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HcSwQTaIOBk</a>"},{"pid":"1a8051a3ee0a6e0c1074f45d8335114b7793f68b","tid":2155872,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:35:40.000Z","msg":"切左粒龍珠佢無咁多病痛"},{"pid":"2a9587db4bd326d0c96993ca903d15a6107f6b21","tid":2155872,"uid":172589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a8051a3ee0a6e0c1074f45d8335114b7793f68b","tid":2155872,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:35:40.000Z","msg":"切左粒龍珠佢無咁多病痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05: